HEADWORD: Parvati
<hw>Parvati</hw> <pos>prop. n.</pos> <fld>(Hinduism)</fld> <def>The wife
of <persfn>Siva</persfn> and a benevolent aspect of
<persfn>Devi</persfn>; the goddess of plenty.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> Anapurna, Annapurna.</syn>⟦br⟧
